4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1707542122&amp;ssig=BING%2Bz3aMw&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4994478629388389" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
